	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'm not sure but I'd double check the "initialization code" is stored somewhere that the SPC file doesn't use, and maybe you should be carefully when initialisating $f0 - $ff values - they are registers and it may be bad if you simply "copy" the values as it from the .spc file. You'd only want to copy the values at $f0, $f1, $f8, $f9 and $fa.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


