		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">That code worked for me in snes9x.</div>
<br />The snes9x I'm talking about here is Geiger's debugger version (1.43?), so they might have improved accuracy since then, which could explain why it doesn't work in snes9x for you.
<br />
<br />Anyway, when I was testing this code on my SNES it seemed like it froze somewhere in the "copy data from RAM to the SPC" inner loop, so something is wrong in the way it communicates with the SPC. I haven't bothered trying to work out a fix yet.

		

